title: War of the Roses: The North Shore Weekend
description: Luke didn't have any reason to suspect his girlfriend Laura was cheating until she was supposed to be in the North Shore for a girl's weekend with her friend but then Luke ran into her friend at Menards.  What is Laura's reasoning for this and is it good enough to prove she wasn't cheating?
